edu.acase.hvz.hvz_app.api.requests

Class BaseReportRequest<ReportModel extends BaseReportModel>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.acase.hvz.hvz_app.api.requests.BaseReportRequest<ReportModel>
  • Type Parameters:
    ReportModel - Which type of ReportModel this should use
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HumanReportRequest, ZombieReportRequest

    public abstract class BaseReportRequest<ReportModel extends BaseReportModel>
extends java.lang.Object
    ReportRequests are used to facilitate transactions with the server. GET, POST, PUT, etc. This is the base used for all specific requests.
